<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonical="https://gummyguide.com/vitamins/best-postnatal-gummies/" ogImage="/images/og/postnatal-gummies.webp" schema={[articleSchema, itemListSchema, faqSchema]}>

  <section class="pg-hero">
    <h1>Best Postnatal Gummies (2026)</h1>
    <p class="pg-sub">We tested 12 postnatal gummies across five criteria — nutrient completeness for postpartum recovery, DHA content, iron inclusion, third-party testing, and value — to find the 7 that best support maternal recovery and breastfeeding nutrition.</p>
