  </section>

  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Vitamins', href: '/vitamins/' }, { label: 'Postnatal Gummies', href: '/vitamins/best-postnatal-gummies/' }]} />

  <div class="w">
    <div class="qp"><div class="qp-label">Our #1 Pick</div><div class="qp-inner"><img src="/images/products/ritual-postnatal.webp" alt="Ritual Essential Postnatal Multivitamin" width="100" height="100" class="qp-img" loading="eager" /><div class="qp-info"><p class="qp-brand">Ritual</p><h3>Ritual Essential Postnatal</h3><p class="qp-reason">350mg algal DHA, choline, methylfolate, iron, and vitamin D3 — the most nutritionally complete postnatal gummy for recovery and breastfeeding. Full ingredient traceability. $2.00/day.</p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0RITUALPOST" class="qp-btn" target="_blank" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div></div>

