    <p>Needed is a practitioner-formulated brand that takes postnatal nutrition more seriously than any mainstream supplement company. Their 300mg choline is the standout — more than triple what most postnatal vitamins provide, addressing the 550mg AI during lactation with a meaningful contribution. The formulation was developed in collaboration with OB/GYNs, midwives, and perinatal nutritionists, and every ingredient is dosed based on clinical evidence for the postpartum period specifically.</p>

    <div class="pcard" id="smartypants-postnatal"><div class="pcard-top"><span class="pcard-badge">Best Tasting</span><span class="pcard-num">#4</span><img src="/images/products/smartypants-postnatal.webp" alt="SmartyPants Postnatal Complete" width="260" height="260" loading="lazy" /></div><div class="pcard-body"><p class="pcard-brand">SmartyPants</p><h3 class="pcard-name">Postnatal Complete</h3><div class="pcard-stars"><span class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span><span class="rating-val">4.5</span><span class="review-ct">(8,901 reviews)</span></div><div class="pcard-specs"><div class="pcard-spec"><strong>DHA</strong><span>240mg (fish oil)</span></div><div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Iron</strong><span>None</span></div><div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Key Nutrients</strong><span>Methylfolate, D3, B12, K2, Zinc</span></div><div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Testing</strong><span>Third-Party (GGMP Certified)</span></div></div><div class="pcard-price"><span class="price">$34.99</span><span class="per-serv">$0.58/day</span></div><div class="pcard-pros-cons"><div class="pcard-pros"><h4>Pros</h4><ul><li>Best-tasting postnatal gummy — lemon creme flavor</li><li>240mg DHA from purified fish oil</li><li>Added K2 for calcium metabolism (unique among postnatals)</li><li>Strong value at $0.58/day</li></ul></div><div class="pcard-cons"><h4>Cons</h4><ul><li>No iron — requires separate supplementation</li><li>Fish oil DHA — not suitable for vegans</li></ul></div></div><div class="pcard-ctas"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0SMARTYPOST" class="btn-cta" target="_blank" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div></div>

    <p>SmartyPants delivers the best-tasting postnatal gummy with meaningful DHA (240mg) and a unique K2 addition. Vitamin K2 supports calcium metabolism — important during the postpartum period when bone mineral density decreases 3-5% during breastfeeding. The methylfolate form ensures optimal folate bioavailability regardless of MTHFR status. The absence of iron means a separate supplement is needed, but the taste and compliance advantages are significant for sleep-deprived new mothers.</p>

    <div class="pcard" id="megafood-postnatal"><div class="pcard-top"><span class="pcard-badge">Best Organic</span><span class="pcard-num">#5</span><img src="/images/products/megafood-postnatal.webp" alt="MegaFood Baby & Me 2 Postnatal" width="260" height="260" loading="lazy" /></div><div class="pcard-body"><p class="pcard-brand">MegaFood</p><h3 class="pcard-name">Baby & Me 2 Postnatal</h3><div class="pcard-stars"><span class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span><span class="rating-val">4.5</span><span class="review-ct">(5,678 reviews)</span></div><div class="pcard-specs"><div class="pcard-spec"><strong>DHA</strong><span>200mg (algal)</span></div><div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Iron</strong><span>18mg (gentle, food-complexed)</span></div><div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Key Nutrients</strong><span>Methylfolate, D3, B12, Choline</span></div><div class="pcard-spec"><strong>Testing</strong><span>NSF Certified, Non-GMO</span></div></div><div class="pcard-price"><span class="price">$45.99</span><span class="per-serv">$1.53/day</span></div><div class="pcard-pros-cons"><div class="pcard-pros"><h4>Pros</h4><ul><li>NSF Certified — rigorous third-party quality testing</li><li>Food-complexed iron for gentle absorption</li><li>Whole-food approach with organic ingredients</li><li>Includes choline for infant brain development support</li></ul></div><div class="pcard-cons"><h4>Cons</h4><ul><li>200mg DHA is lower than Ritual and Needed</li><li>Premium pricing</li></ul></div></div><div class="pcard-ctas"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0MEGAPOST" class="btn-cta" target="_blank" rel="nofollow sponsored noopener">Check Price on Amazon</a></div></div></div>

    <p>MegaFood's Baby & Me 2 Postnatal uses their signature FoodState process — binding nutrients to organic food concentrates for enhanced absorption and gentler delivery. The NSF certification provides one of the most rigorous third-party quality verifications available, and the food-complexed iron minimizes GI side effects.</p>

